<span id="freeTextContainer12764397022717222228">A deceptively simple book of &quot;food rules&quot; which are both thought provoking and amusing-don&apos;t eat food y our grandmother wouldn&apos;t recognize, don&apos;t buy food advertised on TV, don&apos;t buy food that has to advertise that it&apos;s healthy. Not militant, the suggestion is to try making changes in each section. The illustrations by Maira Kalman surely enhance the book. Delightful</span>
  <span id="freeText12764397022717222228" style="display:none">A deceptively simple book of "food rules" which are both thought provoking and amusing-don't eat food y our grandmother wouldn't recognize, don't buy food advertised on TV, don't buy food that has to advertise that it's healthy. Not militant, the suggestion is to try making changes in each section. The illustrations by Maira Kalman surely enhance the book. Delightful</span>
