<span id="freeTextContainer3596840027290839652">Pollan delivers the wisdom of generations of people who eat in pithy, accessible style. Rather than diets or fads, common sense and our grandmother’s wisdom should guide our eating habits. <br/><br/>If you’re buying, make sure you get the edition with Maira Kalman’s delightful illustrations.</span>

